direction: right

Agent Manager: {
  shape: component
  style: {
    fill: "#e2e8f0"
    stroke: "#475569"
    border-radius: 5
  }
}

rules.md: {
  shape: document
  tooltip: Global constraints and instructions
  style: {
    fill: "#fef08a"
    stroke: "#ca8a04"
  }
}

skills/: {
  shape: package
  tooltip: Specialized capabilities
  style: {
    fill: "#bfdbfe"
    stroke: "#2563eb"
  }

  skill_A_module: {
    shape: component
  }
  
  skill_B_module: {
    shape: component
  }
}

# Interactions
rules.md -> Agent Manager: Defines core policies and guardrails
Agent Manager -> rules.md: Reads constraints on initialization

Agent Manager -> skills/: Discovers available skills
skills/ -> Agent Manager: Returns list of capabilities

Agent Manager -> skills/.skill_A_module: Invokes specialized function
skills/.skill_A_module -> Agent Manager: Returns parsed/processed data
